    %h2(style = "margin-top:0") What is Infinispan ?
    Infinispan is a distributed in-memory key/object data store made available under the Apache License 2.0. 
    It can be used both as an embedded Java library and as a language-independent service accessed remotely 
    over a variety of protocols (HotRod, REST and Memcached). It offers advanced functionality such as 
